summary: Hypothesis disproven but deeper insight gained: RecursiveSeed does create non-zero times for temporal witnesses, BUT it also propagates G-formulas TO time 0. The actual blocker is chain architecture: forward/backward chains only support single-direction propagation, lacking cross-chain communication needed for cross-sign coherence.

artifacts.summary: Analysis of RecursiveSeed formula placement showing chain architecture is the true blocker, not seed placement
